headline: Manpower Named a Global Leader and Star Performer in Latest Everest Group PEAK Matrix® Assessment 2025
summary: Manpower®, a global leader in contingent staffing and permanent resourcing and part of the ManpowerGroup (NYSE: MAN) family of brands, has been recognized as both a Leader and Star Performer in Everest Group's 2025 U.S. Contingent Talent and Strategic Solutions PEAK Matrix® Assessment.

headline: Guidehouse Named Industry Leader for Financial Crime and Compliance Operations
summary: Guidehouse, a global AI-led professional services firm, has been named a Leader in the 2025 Everest Group PEAK Matrix® for Financial Crime and Compliance (FCC) Operations Services. The firm stands out among global service providers for its bold strategic vision, exceptional delivery, and powerful market influence.

headline: Startek® joins Everest Group and Clinton Global Initiative to expand inclusive hiring through Impact Sourcing Pledge
summary: Startek®, a digital-first global customer experience (CX) solutions provider, announced its participation in the Clinton Global Initiative (CGI) Impact Sourcing Pledge, led by Everest Group. This global initiative aims to create one million new impact-sourcing jobs by 2030, fostering economic opportunity for historically marginalized communities.

headline: EG Q2 Deep Dive: Portfolio Reshaping and Selective Growth Define Results
summary: Global reinsurance company Everest Group (NYSE:EG) reported revenue ahead of Wall Street’s expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 6.2% year on year to $4.49 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $17.36 per share was 17.1% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
